to prison for 20 years.

04:04.544 --> 04:07.070
That was back in 1939.

04:09.316 --> 04:11.842
He's out!

04:11.952 --> 04:13.317
Clarence!

04:13.420 --> 04:15.479
Did you see anybody
suspicious around?

04:16.690 --> 04:18.658
You know something?

04:18.759 --> 04:21.023
